Text: Episode 2 is nuked at about 1hr 33min in, depending on your media player, either (a) video plays normally but sound goes wonky, or (b) audio plays normally but video speeds up. There is currently no other version of this episode up anywhere and it is not known if a repack is forthcoming ...
